							</h4>
							<p class="text-gray-300">
								Newsletter automation, publishing workflows, and
								audience engagement systems.
							</p>
						</div>
					</div>

					<div
						class="card bg-gradient-to-br from-accent/10 to-transparent border border-accent/20 backdrop-blur-xl"
					>
						<div class="card-body">
