							</h4>
							<p class="text-gray-300 text-lg">
								We dive deep into how you create, what slows you
								down, and where technology can help. Your
								creative process is unique — your systems should
								be too.
							</p>
						</div>
						<div class="md:w-1/2">
							<img
								src="https://images.unsplash.com/photo-1531403009284-440f080d1e12?w=600&h=400&fit=crop"
								alt="Creative workflow discussion"
								class="rounded-xl shadow-2xl w-full"
							/>
						</div>
					</div>

					<div
						class="flex flex-col md:flex-row-reverse gap-8 items-center"
