							</h4>
							<p class="text-gray-300 text-lg">
								We design and build systems that feel intuitive
								and look beautiful. Technology should enhance
								your creativity, not complicate it.
							</p>
						</div>
						<div class="md:w-1/2">
							<img
								src="https://images.unsplash.com/photo-1498050108023-c5249f4df085?w=600&h=400&fit=crop"
