								for you. We provide training, support, and
								ongoing optimization as your creative practice
								evolves.
							</p>
						</div>
						<div class="md:w-1/2">
							<img
								src="https://images.unsplash.com/photo-1522071820081-009f0129c71c?w=600&h=400&fit=crop"
								alt="Creative success"
